<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-107 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  2 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> FRANCE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Pasqua Agrees To Pursue Spanish Terrorists </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Pasqua Agrees To Pursue Spanish Terrorists </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0206141494 Madrid RNE International in Spanish 1300 GMT 2 
Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0206141494 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid RNE International </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] [Spanish] Justice and Interior Minister Juan Alberto 
Belloch agreed in Paris with his French colleague, Charles 
Pasqua, to continue applying official pressure so that 
terrorists hiding in that country are arrested. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

