<H4>    Depart For Corfu Summit </H4>

<F P=102> LD0706095794 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 0900 GMT 
7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0706095794 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


