<H3> <TI>   Saxony-Anhalt Republicans Run in 26 Jun Election </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Saxony-Anhalt Republicans Run in 26 Jun Election </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0606123994 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 0950 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0606123994 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DDP/ADN </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Magdeburg (DDP/ADN) -- The Republicans' list of 
candidates for election to the state parliament of Saxony-Anhalt 
has now been accepted for the 26 June elections. This follows 
the Saxony-Anhalt Electoral Committee today revizing its 
decision adopted last Wednesday [1 June], by one vote. 
Following detailed discussion, four of the seven members of the 
committee voted to recognize the list. Only the Christian 
Democratic Union stuck to its decision not to admit the 
Republicans. The Social Democratic Party and the Party of 
Democratic Socialists abstained and Alliance-90/Greens changed 
their decision. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

