<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Statistic Show May Inflation Rate 10 Percent </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0406113494 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 4 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0406113494 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
