<H3> <TI>   Brussels Review Recommends Improving Trade Benefits </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Brussels Review Recommends Improving Trade Benefits </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0306091094 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 3 Jun 94 p 
6--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM0306091094 </F>
<F P=104>  London FINANCIAL TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


