  [Text] Hamburg (DPA) -- Hamburg lawyer Mike Bashford, 36, 
has become the new federal chairman of the Instead Party. 
Bashford was elected chief of the Instead Party at a federal 
delegates meeting in Hamburg on Saturday [4 June]. He received 
